{"tid":1687404,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"面對今日嘅香港，睇完好感動嘅一套戲…","createTime":"2019-11-01T20:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T15:18:29.000Z","uid":12661,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"af3218b8e57efe14b77a51d9a7c3c1bf461d1d27","tid":1687404,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T20:44:25.000Z","msg":"噚日偶然喺 movie movie 睇咗2006年嘅一套電影 The wind that shakes the barley （風吹麥動）&hellip; 故事講述100年前（約1919年），愛爾蘭人民面對英國紀律差劣嘅臨時部隊：Black and Tans<br />\n<br />\nBlack and Tans 大部分來自第一次世界大戰之後嘅退役失業軍人，為咗錢，受英國招募，前往愛爾蘭協助當時英國管理愛爾蘭嘅軍隊/警隊（RIC），鎮壓爭取民主獨立嘅愛爾蘭人&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nBlack and Tans 唔算精良部隊，喺愛爾蘭用濫捕濫殺嘅手段，故意製造恐怖，試圖令愛爾蘭嘅抗爭者屈服&hellip; 係咪似曾相識呢？<br />\n<br />\nYouTube 有電影嘅部分片段，大家睇完，覺得點呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/681r4jC4apk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F681r4jC4apk&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8AwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=332dc25d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/681r4jC4apk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-maEh8eax3I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-maEh8eax3I&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8AwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=fd6b3749\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-maEh8eax3I</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7XJ772_d3-Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7XJ772_d3-Y&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8AwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=07968aa6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7XJ772_d3-Y</a>"},{"pid":"b5025b4774e2d1f48a1c6dbf548246d130724656","tid":1687404,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T20:56:19.000Z","msg":"半夜開喺影視台，應該幾難有巴打絲打睇到㗎啦，唯有自推一下先啦&hellip;"},{"pid":"b0f80f16f83bd1b5e1ca596ec0d2d1a41c1831e4","tid":1687404,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T20:58:40.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"723dfd0f907817b8171849720aea22eda9591aed","tid":1687404,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep